tools.description:
Retrieve the entire list of all products in the store with status "active" or "available".

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": List[ProductInfo]
    }
    or
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str
    }

Constraints:
    - Only products where status is "active" or "available" (case-insensitive) are included.
